      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental conditions are fully documented. Inlet flow rates matched to ±1.2%, rotational speeds to ±0.8%, and blood analog viscosity to ±3.1%. Temperature was maintained at 37°C ± 0.5°C in both experiment and simulation. Hematocrit of 40% assumed uniform."
