      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index predictions compared against three independent in-vitro datasets. Validation metric E% ranged from 2.1% to 8.4% across five operating points, all within the combined validation uncertainty of ±12%. PIV velocity comparisons showed mean absolute error of 4.7% against published benchmark data."
