      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares impeller topology with the subject device. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB range (2.5–5.0 L/min, 2000–3000 RPM). Glycerol-water blood analog (viscosity 3.5 mPa·s) is within 8% of clinical blood viscosity at 37°C."
