      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal use-error assessment is not required. Simulation engineers hold CFD practitioner certifications and completed internal training on hemolysis modeling protocols. Independent peer review of simulation setup was conducted by a senior analyst not involved in primary simulation execution."
